{"tid":1536312,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"平野鈴子真係真女神","createTime":"2019-09-03T15:28:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-05T15:24:06.000Z","uid":89530,"like":101,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":39,"replies":[{"pid":"b4cc168a405753e214e19994e9609b5185c88806","tid":1536312,"uid":89530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T15:28:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YQwfHSe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYQwfHSe.jpg&h=bef5cec9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aygn7iZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Faygn7iZ.jpg&h=996cd5e2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ORS27iV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FORS27iV.jpg&h=f9005b3b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xF4AHSg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxF4AHSg.jpg&h=8d950fcc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/t7tedYX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ft7tedYX.jpg&h=5a865854&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n人哋一直都同香港人行得好近<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />多謝企喺香港人呢邊，好想瘋狂同女神講多謝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />雖然應該好多人都follow咗佢，但都想開post多謝佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n見隔離有人開post讚隻狗乸靚，咁撚樣都叫靚，屌啦，為嗰啲臭錢去做狗，有理想一早resign咗啦屌。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n光復香港，時代革命。<br />\n五大訴求，缺一不可。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7dBrPzQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7dBrPzQ.png&h=17711c7c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RYmjp8b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRYmjp8b.png&h=95b16da1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"800c9693c660b9d3e2b5c490155058096398c994","tid":1536312,"uid":123991,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T15:29:51.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月7日 (六) 1PM<br />\n機場交通壓力測試 (重考)</strong></div><br />\n<br />\n香港市民：<br />\n✅ 以遊客身份入機場觀賞飛機升降 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 唔識路就坐多幾轉車 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 必需繳付車資乘坐黨鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n烏克蘭, 法國等其他國藉居民：<br />\n各有各做, 自由發揮, 唔割但要小心 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n另外可參考唔揸春袋揸輸精管方法: <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n [行動post] 肯入黎睇9.7點樣揸機場輸精管未 | LIHKG <br />\n <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1</a> <br />\n <br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nyixFQQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnyixFQQ.png&h=cc1f24a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月8日 (日) 2PM<br />\n香港人權與民主法案集會<br />\n美國駐港澳總領事館</strong></div><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2GKH20p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2GKH20p.png&h=6178433f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"81b4fb68901da410c959fb08df1c26530007c077","tid":1536312,"uid":167883,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T15:31:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Renq43y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRenq43y.jpg&h=bb73b46e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/X2FTuve.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FX2FTuve.jpg&h=3a22dffd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xbetioz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2